.DS_Store

# GPAO-T generated evidence hygiene.
# Keep curated Markdown/JSON evidence files explicit, but do not flood git with
# raw copied live runtime backups or repeated generated run directories.
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-backups/**
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-backups/**/
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-backups/**/manifest.json
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-*-patch/**
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-*-patch/**/
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-*-patch/**/manifest.json
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-test-session-cleanup/**
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-test-session-cleanup/**/
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-test-session-cleanup/**/manifest.json
docs/03-verification/evidence/conversation-ux-qa/*.json

# Raw live/runtime repair snapshots are retained on disk but should not dominate
# normal source review. Curated Markdown/JSON summaries in the evidence root stay
# visible and should reference these folders when needed.
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-device-repair-backup-*/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-runtime-repair-*/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-conversation-qa-*/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-plugin-allowlist/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-hook-preview/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-patch-stage/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-namespace-migration/**
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-namespace-migration/
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-namespace-migration/manifest.json
docs/03-verification/evidence/runtime-workspace-absorption-*/backups/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/**/*.before

# Heavy generated runtime/browser rebuild evidence stays local. Keep curated
# root-level Markdown/JSON evidence and screenshots when they are intentionally
# referenced by release notes.
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-standalone-namespace-rebuild/**
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-standalone-namespace-rebuild/
!docs/03-verification/evidence/live-standalone-namespace-rebuild/manifest.json
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-chat-layout-recovery-hotfix/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/live-dashboard-cache-bust-hotfix/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/final-stage-6-visual-qa-*/runtime-lock-recovery/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/git-hygiene-backups/**
docs/03-verification/evidence/**/*.backup
docs/03-verification/evidence/**/*.sqlite.before-*

# Accidental scratch files from terminal experiments.
console.log(yaml ok))
